        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size:20px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500;">Talks at Notre Dame</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">French President Emmanuel Macron hosted <a href="https://www.france24.com/en/france/20241207-macron-trump-zelensky-hold-trilateral-on-sidelines-of-notre-dame-ceremony" target="_blank">trilateral talks</a> in Paris with Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky and U.S. President-elect Donald Trump on the sidelines of the Notre Dame Cathedral reopening ceremony. The meeting addressed global concerns, focusing on Trump’s approach to U.S. military aid for Ukraine amid its ongoing conflict with Russia. Macron proposed the meeting, emphasizing unity, while Zelensky <a href="https://twitter.com/ZelenskyyUa/status/1865451236482310227?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1865451236482310227%7Ctwgr%5E96d2159c2d6bd6419b29ee900d703bfcfe635a70%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Ffrance%2F20241207-macron-trump-zelensky-hold-trilateral-on-sidelines-of-notre-dame-ceremony" target="_blank">expressed</a> optimism about productive collaboration.</p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">Trump pledged to resolve the war swiftly within a day of assuming office and named Lt. Gen. Keith Kellogg a special envoy to mandate a truce. Kellogg has proposed a plan to Trump to end the war, but a Russian tycoon expressed that Russia will not take his plans until it addresses its security concerns. The trilateral talks were mainly European efforts to secure U.S. support under Trump’s forthcoming presidency. Just a few hours after this conversation, Trump <a href="https://eu.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2024/12/08/trump-ukraine-ceasefire-russia-zelenskyy/76849858007/" target="_blank">called</a> for a ceasefire between Ukraine and Russia.</p>
        </mj-text>
